{"id":17983,"date":"2022-12-31T04:22:35","date_gmt":"2022-12-31T04:22:35","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/nd.wv3.net\/amg-car\/khach-hang-phai-boc-tham-de-mua-xe-toyota.html"},"modified":"2022-12-31T04:22:35","modified_gmt":"2022-12-31T04:22:35","slug":"khach-hang-phai-boc-tham-de-mua-xe-toyota","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/2022\/12\/31\/khach-hang-phai-boc-tham-de-mua-xe-toyota\/","title":{"rendered":"Kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng ph\u1ea3i b\u1ed1c th\u0103m \u0111\u1ec3 mua xe Toyota"},"content":{"rendered":"<\/p>\n<div class=\"entry-content\">\n<p><span class=\"location-stamp\">Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n<\/span><br \/>\nNgu\u1ed3n cung c\u1ea5p ph\u1ee5 t\u00f9ng thi\u1ebfu h\u1ee5t d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf v\u00e0 Toyota ph\u1ea3i ngh\u0129 c\u00e1ch b\u00e1n GR Corolla m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">GR Corolla b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1n ra th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng trong n\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 2\/12 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nh\u01b0 h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft c\u00e1c m\u1eabu xe kh\u00e1c.  Kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ea1i l\u00fd v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7t xe nh\u01b0 h\u00e3ng Nh\u1eadt t\u1eebng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 7, khi ra m\u1eaft hothatch.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch nh\u1eadp s\u1ed1 v\u00e0 con s\u1ed1 may m\u1eafn s\u1ebd mang v\u1ec1 cho ch\u1ee7 s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc GR Corolla mua.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"680x0\" alt=\"Toyota GR Corolla v\u1edbi v\u1ebb ngo\u00e0i h\u1ea7m h\u1ed1, c\u00f4ng su\u1ea5t g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i Corolla th\u01b0\u1eddng.  \u1ea2nh: TOYOTA\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/khach-hang-phai-boc-tham-de-mua-xe-toyota.jpg\" title=\"khach-hang-phai-boc-tham-de-mua-xe-toyota\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/khach-hang-phai-boc-tham-de-mua-xe-toyota-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/khach-hang-phai-boc-tham-de-mua-xe-toyota-600x360.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/khach-hang-phai-boc-tham-de-mua-xe-toyota.jpg 680w\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Image\">Toyota GR Corolla v\u1edbi v\u1ebb ngo\u00e0i h\u1ea7m h\u1ed1, c\u00f4ng su\u1ea5t g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i Corolla th\u01b0\u1eddng.  \u1ea2nh: TOYOTA<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p h\u01a1n th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ec7 b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfc GR Corolla \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1n ra ch\u1ec9 gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n 500 chi\u1ebfc cho b\u1ea3n ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n v\u00e0 70 chi\u1ebfc cho b\u1ea3n Morizo \u200b\u200bEdition.  So v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n th\u01b0\u1eddng, b\u1ea3n cao c\u1ea5p ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 hai ch\u1ed7 ng\u1ed3i v\u00e0 m\u00f4-men xo\u1eafn t\u0103ng th\u00eam 30 Nm.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Ng\u00e0y 6\/1\/2023, 70 ng\u01b0\u1eddi may m\u1eafn c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i mua GR Corolla Morizo \u200b\u200bEdition s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1.  Danh s\u00e1ch 500 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 sau \u0111\u00e2y m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y.  Vi\u1ec7c giao h\u00e0ng cho c\u1ea3 hai phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn \u200b\u200b\u200b\u200bs\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0o m\u00f9a xu\u00e2n t\u1edbi.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">V\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, c\u1ea3 hai phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng chung \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 x\u0103ng 1.6 turbo, 3 xi-lanh, h\u1ed9p s\u1ed1 iMT 6 c\u1ea5p, b\u1ed9 vi sai h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1ee3t Torsen v\u00e0 h\u1ec7 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ed9ng 4 b\u00e1nh GR-Four.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"680x0\" alt=\"Hai phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n kh\u00e1c nhau v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 ch\u1ed7 ng\u1ed3i, th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 m\u00f4-men xo\u1eafn v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tinh ch\u1ec9nh kh\u00e1c.  \u1ea2nh: TOYOTA\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672436524_254_khach-hang-phai-boc-tham-de-mua-xe-toyota.jpg\" title=\"1672436524_254_khach-hang-phai-boc-tham-de-mua-xe-toyota\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672436524_254_khach-hang-phai-boc-tham-de-mua-xe-toyota-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672436524_254_khach-hang-phai-boc-tham-de-mua-xe-toyota-600x338.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672436524_254_khach-hang-phai-boc-tham-de-mua-xe-toyota.jpg 680w\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Image\">Hai phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n kh\u00e1c nhau v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 ch\u1ed7 ng\u1ed3i, th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 m\u00f4-men xo\u1eafn v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tinh ch\u1ec9nh kh\u00e1c.  \u1ea2nh: TOYOTA<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">\u0110i\u1ec3m kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Corolla GR ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng su\u1ea5t 300 m\u00e3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ea1i 6.500 v\u00f2ng\/ph\u00fat v\u00e0 m\u00f4-men xo\u1eafn 370 Nm t\u1ea1i 3.000-5.550 v\u00f2ng\/ph\u00fat.  Phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n Morizo \u200b\u200bc\u00f3 c\u00f9ng m\u00e3 l\u1ef1c, nh\u01b0ng m\u00f4-men xo\u1eafn l\u00e0 400 Nm t\u1ea1i 3.250-4.600 v\u00f2ng\/ph\u00fat.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, do ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 hai ch\u1ed7 ng\u1ed3i n\u00ean phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n cao c\u1ea5p h\u01a1n nh\u1eb9 h\u01a1n 30 kg, v\u1edbi tr\u1ecdng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng 1.470 kg.  M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tinh ch\u1ec9nh kh\u00e1c n\u1eb1m \u1edf c\u1ea3n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, la-z\u0103ng h\u1ee3p kim gia c\u01b0\u1eddng BBS 18 inch v\u00e0 l\u1ed1p r\u1ed9ng h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">T\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, Toyota GR Corolla c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 kh\u1edfi \u0111i\u1ec3m 38.900 USD, trong khi phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n Morizo \u200b\u200bc\u00f3 gi\u00e1 53.000 USD.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align:right;\">M\u1ef9 Anh (theo Motor1)<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align:right\"><strong>AMGCAR.VN<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/p><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n Ngu\u1ed3n cung c\u1ea5p ph\u1ee5 t\u00f9ng thi\u1ebfu h\u1ee5t d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf v\u00e0 Toyota ph\u1ea3i ngh\u0129 c\u00e1ch b\u00e1n GR Corolla m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. GR Corolla b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1n ra th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng trong n\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 2\/12 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nh\u01b0 h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft c\u00e1c m\u1eabu xe [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":16524,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[75],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/17983"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=17983"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/17983\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/16524"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=17983"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=17983"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=17983"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/a